          .hero__course-intro
            p Get set for a career in a sector with amazing opportunities. Our degrees in real estate and quantity surveying are accredited by internationally recognised bodies, giving you a head start in this fast-growing industry. 
            p Get the best of both worlds – choose from a real estate course that will provide a direct pathway into a career as a surveyor or realtor, or a quantity surveying course with built-in industry experience that provides a great basis for quantity surveying and project management jobs. Either option gives you the opportunity to study in the UK for part of your degree. 
          
          a.btn.red(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/apply') How to apply
      
      section.course__container
