          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            h2.course__heading 
              em BSc 
              | Real Estate
            p Develop an in-depth understanding of the core areas of real estate such as economics, finance, planning, valuation, law and construction to prepare you for a range of careers. This flexible degree, delivered by the world-renowned Henley Business School, lets you choose your specialism in your final year to tailor your degree to your own interests, as well as providing the opportunity to study in the UK. 
            p Accredited by the internationally recognised Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors (RICS), Royal Institution of Surveyors Malaysia (RISM) and the Board of Valuers, Appraisers and Estate Agents Malaysia (BOVAEA), it’s also rated #1 in the UK and provides a direct route into careers in property and planning. Typical roles include chartered surveyor, project manager and asset manager. 
            a.btn.red(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/apply') How to apply
            a.btn.grey(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/bsc-real-estate') Find out more
